      public void create(String cineplexName, String code, SeatPlan seatingPlan)
      Create a new Cinema and appends it to cineplex arraylist Attributes are validated before creation If invalid attributes are thrown, throws error and do nothing If database file does not exist, a new data file is create and saved else new cinema is added to the database under the cineplex choosen
      Parameters:
      cineplexName - Name of cineplex that the new cinemas is to be added
      code - New cinemas' code
      seatingPlan - New cinemas' seat plan
